{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":496,"text":"There is something you know about me,"},{"time":4255,"text":"something very personal,"},{"time":8095,"text":"and there is something\nI know about every one of you"},{"time":12550,"text":"and that's very central to your concerns."},{"time":16663,"text":"There is something that we know"},{"time":19268,"text":"about everyone we meet\nanywhere in the world, on the street,"},{"time":25326,"text":"that is the very mainspring\nof whatever they do"},{"time":30304,"text":"and whatever they put up with."},{"time":34047,"text":"And that is that all of us\nwant to be happy."},{"time":40341,"text":"In this, we are all together."},{"time":43203,"text":"How we imagine our happiness,\nthat differs from one another,"},{"time":48701,"text":"but it's already a lot\nthat we have all in common,"},{"time":53529,"text":"that we want to be happy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":57164,"text":"Now my topic is gratefulness."},{"time":60612,"text":"What is the connection\nbetween happiness and gratefulness?"},{"time":67310,"text":"Many people would say,\nwell, that's very easy."},{"time":70328,"text":"When you are happy, you are grateful."},{"time":74331,"text":"But think again."},{"time":77688,"text":"Is it really the happy people\nthat are grateful?"},{"time":83077,"text":"We all know quite a number of people"},{"time":86642,"text":"who have everything\nthat it would take to be happy,"},{"time":90843,"text":"and they are not happy,"},{"time":92624,"text":"because they want something else\nor they want more of the same."},{"time":98173,"text":"And we all know people\nwho have lots of misfortune,"},{"time":105021,"text":"misfortune that we ourselves\nwould not want to have,"},{"time":108822,"text":"and they are deeply happy."},{"time":111574,"text":"They radiate happiness. You are surprised."},{"time":115017,"text":"Why? Because they are grateful."},{"time":118348,"text":"So it is not happiness\nthat makes us grateful."},{"time":122407,"text":"It's gratefulness that makes us happy."},{"time":125835,"text":"If you think it's happiness\nthat makes you grateful,"},{"time":128776,"text":"think again."},{"time":130285,"text":"It's gratefulness that makes you happy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":134293,"text":"Now, we can ask,"},{"time":136805,"text":"what do we really mean by gratefulness?"},{"time":140897,"text":"And how does it work?"},{"time":145985,"text":"I appeal to your own experience."},{"time":147975,"text":"We all know from experience how it goes."},{"time":151055,"text":"We experience something\nthat's valuable to us."},{"time":156734,"text":"Something is given to us\nthat's valuable to us."},{"time":161925,"text":"And it's really given."},{"time":163871,"text":"These two things have to come together."},{"time":166114,"text":"It has to be something valuable,\nand it's a real gift."},{"time":171727,"text":"You haven't bought it.\nYou haven't earned it."},{"time":174894,"text":"You haven't traded it in.\nYou haven't worked for it."},{"time":177369,"text":"It's just given to you."},{"time":178821,"text":"And when these two things come together,"},{"time":181088,"text":"something that's really valuable to me\nand I realize it's freely given,"},{"time":186737,"text":"then gratefulness spontaneously\nrises in my heart,"},{"time":191674,"text":"happiness spontaneously rises in my heart."},{"time":196037,"text":"That's how gratefulness happens."}]},{"cues":[{"time":199546,"text":"Now the key to all this"},{"time":204965,"text":"is that we cannot only\nexperience this once in a while."},{"time":212997,"text":"We cannot only have grateful experiences."},{"time":216755,"text":"We can be people who live gratefully."},{"time":220649,"text":"Grateful living, that is the thing."},{"time":224216,"text":"And how can we live gratefully?"},{"time":228136,"text":"By experiencing, by becoming aware"},{"time":232520,"text":"that every moment\nis a given moment, as we say."},{"time":237293,"text":"It's a gift. You haven't earned it."},{"time":239898,"text":"You haven't brought it about in any way."},{"time":242805,"text":"You have no way of assuring"},{"time":245917,"text":"that there will be\nanother moment given to you,"},{"time":248917,"text":"and yet, that's the most valuable thing\nthat can ever be given to us,"},{"time":254006,"text":"this moment, with all the opportunity\nthat it contains."},{"time":259518,"text":"If we didn't have this present moment,"},{"time":262182,"text":"we wouldn't have\nany opportunity to do anything"},{"time":265382,"text":"or experience anything,"},{"time":267230,"text":"and this moment is a gift."},{"time":269242,"text":"It's a given moment, as we say."}]},{"cues":[{"time":271712,"text":"Now, we say the gift within this gift\nis really the opportunity."},{"time":278352,"text":"What you are really grateful for\nis the opportunity,"},{"time":282918,"text":"not the thing that is given to you,"},{"time":284876,"text":"because if that thing were somewhere else"},{"time":286855,"text":"and you didn't have\nthe opportunity to enjoy it,"},{"time":290385,"text":"to do something with it,"},{"time":292220,"text":"you wouldn't be grateful for it."},{"time":295149,"text":"Opportunity is the gift within every gift,"},{"time":299169,"text":"and we have this saying,\nopportunity knocks only once."},{"time":305943,"text":"Well, think again."},{"time":308679,"text":"Every moment is a new gift,\nover and over again,"},{"time":312890,"text":"and if you miss the opportunity\nof this moment,"},{"time":316158,"text":"another moment is given to us,\nand another moment."},{"time":320175,"text":"We can avail ourselves\nof this opportunity,"},{"time":322889,"text":"or we can miss it,"},{"time":324760,"text":"and if we avail ourselves\nof the opportunity,"},{"time":328694,"text":"it is the key to happiness."},{"time":331511,"text":"Behold the master key to our happiness"},{"time":334776,"text":"in our own hands."},{"time":336579,"text":"Moment by moment,\nwe can be grateful for this gift."}]},{"cues":[{"time":341593,"text":"Does that mean"},{"time":344116,"text":"that we can be grateful for everything?"},{"time":347629,"text":"Certainly not."},{"time":349597,"text":"We cannot be grateful\nfor violence, for war,"},{"time":354537,"text":"for oppression, for exploitation."},{"time":357360,"text":"On the personal level,\nwe cannot be grateful"},{"time":360123,"text":"for the loss of a friend,\nfor unfaithfulness,"},{"time":363424,"text":"for bereavement."},{"time":366733,"text":"But I didn't say\nwe can be grateful for everything."},{"time":370527,"text":"I said we can be grateful\nin every given moment"},{"time":375033,"text":"for the opportunity,"},{"time":376887,"text":"and even when we are confronted\nwith something that is terribly difficult,"},{"time":383306,"text":"we can rise to this occasion"},{"time":385846,"text":"and respond to the opportunity\nthat is given to us."},{"time":390101,"text":"It isn't as bad as it might seem."},{"time":392476,"text":"Actually, when you look at it\nand experience it,"},{"time":396369,"text":"you find that most of the time,"},{"time":399325,"text":"what is given to us\nis the opportunity to enjoy,"},{"time":403058,"text":"and we only miss it\nbecause we are rushing through life"},{"time":406099,"text":"and we are not stopping\nto see the opportunity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":409919,"text":"But once in a while,"},{"time":411350,"text":"something very difficult is given to us,"},{"time":414296,"text":"and when this difficult thing\noccurs to us,"},{"time":418387,"text":"it's a challenge to rise\nto that opportunity,"},{"time":422715,"text":"and we can rise to it\nby learning something"},{"time":426135,"text":"which is sometimes painful."},{"time":427876,"text":"Learning patience, for instance."},{"time":429963,"text":"We have been told that the road to peace"},{"time":432960,"text":"is not a sprint,\nbut is more like a marathon."},{"time":436728,"text":"That takes patience. That's difficult."},{"time":440439,"text":"It may be to stand up for your opinion,\nto stand up for your conviction."},{"time":447126,"text":"That's an opportunity that is given to us."},{"time":450314,"text":"To learn, to suffer, to stand up,"},{"time":453763,"text":"all these opportunities are given to us,"},{"time":456133,"text":"but they are opportunities,"},{"time":457639,"text":"and those who avail themselves\nof those opportunities"},{"time":461515,"text":"are the ones that we admire."},{"time":463642,"text":"They make something out of life."},{"time":465914,"text":"And those who fail\nget another opportunity."},{"time":471023,"text":"We always get another opportunity."},{"time":473240,"text":"That's the wonderful richness of life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":478272,"text":"So how can we find a method\nthat will harness this?"},{"time":484821,"text":"How can each one of us find a method\nfor living gratefully,"},{"time":489851,"text":"not just once in a while being grateful,"},{"time":491780,"text":"but moment by moment to be grateful."},{"time":494591,"text":"How can we do it?\nIt's a very simple method."},{"time":497967,"text":"It's so simple that it's actually\nwhat we were told as children"},{"time":503054,"text":"when we learned to cross the street."},{"time":505882,"text":"Stop."},{"time":507421,"text":"Look."},{"time":508646,"text":"Go."},{"time":509871,"text":"That's all."},{"time":511270,"text":"But how often do we stop?"},{"time":513982,"text":"We rush through life. We don't stop."},{"time":516751,"text":"We miss the opportunity\nbecause we don't stop."},{"time":521012,"text":"We have to stop."},{"time":523883,"text":"We have to get quiet."},{"time":526128,"text":"And we have to build\nstop signs into our lives."}]},{"cues":[{"time":531628,"text":"When I was in Africa\nsome years ago and then came back,"},{"time":536620,"text":"I noticed water."},{"time":539114,"text":"In Africa where I was,\nI didn't have drinkable water."},{"time":543293,"text":"Every time I turned on the faucet,\nI was overwhelmed."},{"time":548067,"text":"Every time I clicked on the light,\nI was so grateful."},{"time":551676,"text":"It made me so happy."},{"time":553241,"text":"But after a while, this wears off."},{"time":555248,"text":"So I put little stickers\non the light switch"},{"time":559034,"text":"and on the water faucet,"},{"time":560735,"text":"and every time I turned it on, water."},{"time":563817,"text":"So leave it up to your own imagination."},{"time":566697,"text":"You can find whatever works best for you,"},{"time":568674,"text":"but you need stop signs in your life."},{"time":572278,"text":"And when you stop,"},{"time":574229,"text":"then the next thing is to look."},{"time":576730,"text":"You look. You open your eyes."},{"time":578985,"text":"You open your ears. You open your nose."},{"time":581271,"text":"You open all your senses"},{"time":583691,"text":"for this wonderful richness\nthat is given to us."},{"time":587326,"text":"There is no end to it,\nand that is what life is all about,"},{"time":591302,"text":"to enjoy, to enjoy what is given to us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":594932,"text":"And then we can also open our hearts,"},{"time":597775,"text":"our hearts for the opportunities,"},{"time":600621,"text":"for the opportunities also to help others,"},{"time":603863,"text":"to make others happy,"},{"time":605158,"text":"because nothing makes us more happy\nthan when all of us are happy."},{"time":610743,"text":"And when we open\nour hearts to the opportunities,"},{"time":614901,"text":"the opportunities invite us\nto do something,"},{"time":618541,"text":"and that is the third."},{"time":619888,"text":"Stop, look, and then go,\nand really do something."},{"time":624351,"text":"And what we can do"},{"time":625955,"text":"is whatever life offers to you\nin that present moment."},{"time":630641,"text":"Mostly it's the opportunity to enjoy,"},{"time":635708,"text":"but sometimes\nit's something more difficult."}]},{"cues":[{"time":639108,"text":"But whatever it is,\nif we take this opportunity,"},{"time":643400,"text":"we go with it, we are creative,\nthose are the creative people."},{"time":648871,"text":"And that little stop, look, go,"},{"time":652744,"text":"is such a potent seed"},{"time":654998,"text":"that it can revolutionize our world."},{"time":658500,"text":"Because we are at the present moment"},{"time":663820,"text":"in the middle of a change\nof consciousness,"},{"time":667156,"text":"and you will be surprised if you --"},{"time":670002,"text":"I am always surprised\nwhen I hear how many times"},{"time":672688,"text":"this word \"gratefulness\"\nand \"gratitude\" comes up."},{"time":675952,"text":"Everywhere you find it,"},{"time":677290,"text":"a grateful airline,\na restaurant gratefulness,"},{"time":680569,"text":"a café gratefulness,\na wine that is gratefulness."},{"time":683778,"text":"Yes, I have even come across\na toilet paper"},{"time":687053,"text":"whose brand is called \"Thank You.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":689420,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":691040,"text":"There is a wave of gratefulness"},{"time":693006,"text":"because people are becoming aware\nhow important this is"},{"time":696812,"text":"and how this can change our world."},{"time":699884,"text":"It can change our world\nin immensely important ways,"},{"time":706524,"text":"because if you're grateful,\nyou're not fearful,"},{"time":710135,"text":"and if you're not fearful,\nyou're not violent."},{"time":713521,"text":"If you're grateful,\nyou act out of a sense of enough"},{"time":717707,"text":"and not of a sense of scarcity,"},{"time":719801,"text":"and you are willing to share."},{"time":721850,"text":"If you are grateful,"},{"time":723142,"text":"you are enjoying\nthe differences between people,"},{"time":726017,"text":"and you are respectful to everybody,"},{"time":728396,"text":"and that changes this power pyramid\nunder which we live."}]},{"cues":[{"time":732129,"text":"And it doesn't make for equality,\nbut it makes for equal respect,"},{"time":737157,"text":"and that is the important thing."},{"time":739161,"text":"The future of the world will be a network,"},{"time":742861,"text":"not a pyramid turned upside down."},{"time":746511,"text":"The revolution of which I am speaking\nis a nonviolent revolution,"},{"time":751023,"text":"and it's so revolutionary\nthat it even revolutionizes"},{"time":754912,"text":"the very concept of a revolution,"},{"time":757093,"text":"because the normal revolution"},{"time":759354,"text":"is one where the power pyramid\nis turned upside down"},{"time":762362,"text":"and those who were on the bottom\nare now on the top"},{"time":765531,"text":"and are doing exactly the same thing\nthat the ones before."},{"time":770246,"text":"What we need is a networking\nof smaller groups,"},{"time":774582,"text":"smaller and smaller groups\nwho know one another,"},{"time":778252,"text":"who interact with one another,\nand that is a grateful world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":782823,"text":"A grateful world\nis a world of joyful people."},{"time":786971,"text":"Grateful people are joyful people,"},{"time":789642,"text":"and joyful people --"},{"time":791683,"text":"the more and more joyful people there are,"},{"time":794446,"text":"the more and more\nwe'll have a joyful world."},{"time":798758,"text":"We have a network for grateful living,\nand it has mushroomed."},{"time":804829,"text":"We couldn't understand why it mushroomed."},{"time":807276,"text":"We have an opportunity\nfor people to light a candle"},{"time":810612,"text":"when they are grateful for something."},{"time":813217,"text":"And there have been\n15 million candles lit in one decade."},{"time":820072,"text":"People are becoming aware\nthat a grateful world is a happy world,"},{"time":826297,"text":"and we all have the opportunity\nby the simple stop, look, go,"},{"time":832323,"text":"to transform the world,\nto make it a happy place."},{"time":836059,"text":"And that is what I hope for us,"},{"time":837561,"text":"and if this has contributed a little\nto making you want to do the same,"},{"time":842459,"text":"stop, look, go."}]},{"cues":[{"time":844121,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":845314,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}